    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>This demo will be updated regularly.</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in an <strong>alternate history where the empires of Kemet (Ancient Nubia-Egypt) remained unconquered</strong>, the <i>Kemet X Demo</i> offers a <strong>first glimpse</strong> into a world where <strong>ancient power meets futuristic warfare</strong>. Experience <strong>fast-paced space battles, third-person melee combat, and educational segments</strong> that uncover the <strong>rich history and languages of Ancient Nubia and Egypt</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/4b83143d84cfe0e795d09b84bef9fe91.poster.avif?t=1752415736\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/4b83143d84cfe0e795d09b84bef9fe91.webm?t=1752415736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/4b83143d84cfe0e795d09b84bef9fe91.mp4?t=1752415736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the world of <strong>warrior-prince Jaraqo</strong> and face the <strong>tyranny of Lord Isfet</strong>, a galactic overlord threatening the future of Kemet's interstellar empire</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/d63ba79020c9dd5aed18ce9377b5b0da.poster.avif?t=1752415736\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/d63ba79020c9dd5aed18ce9377b5b0da.webm?t=1752415736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/d63ba79020c9dd5aed18ce9377b5b0da.mp4?t=1752415736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features in the Demo:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Fast-Paced Space Combat</strong> – Pilot a spacecraft and <strong>engage in explosive combat</strong> across the Kemet X galaxy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Third-Person Melee Combat</strong> – Fight on foot as <strong>warrior-prince Jaraqo</strong>, using <strong>weapons, tactics, and abilities</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Educational Segments</strong> – Learn about the <strong>real history of Ancient Nubia and Egypt</strong>, their rulers and enduring legacies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Ancient Languages</strong> – Experience <strong>Nobiin</strong>, one of the world’s most ancient living languages, through in-game segments designed to preserve and showcase Africa’s linguistic heritage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Rich Sci-Fi Setting</strong> – Explore an <strong>Afrofuturistic vision of Kemet</strong>, blending mythology, advanced technology, and interstellar warfare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>PC &amp; VR Support</strong> – Play in <strong>PC mode</strong> or <strong>VR via Virtual Desktop</strong> for a fully immersive experience, using an <strong>Xbox controller or keyboard</strong>. For the best performance, we recommend <strong>playing in VR on a large screen via Virtual Desktop with an Ethernet connection</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/050047ca532732f11374f3c496039c17.avif?t=1752415736\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras_big/050047ca532732f11374f3c496039c17.avif?t=1752415736 width=800 height=456 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✔️ <strong>A solo-developed creation</strong>: Crafted by indie developer Theo Dusu, <i>Kemet X</i> delivers a captivating journey with an unforgettable ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras/58ab3136482e9e0560d7200d8ff5f698.avif?t=1752415736\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278630/extras_big/58ab3136482e9e0560d7200d8ff5f698.avif?t=1752415736 width=800 height=448 /></span></p>",
